title: Clean Code : Long Title Edition 4th Edition (King of Spades)
content:
Clean Code is a book that teaches programmers how to write better and more maintainable code. It explains the importance of clarity and simplicity in every part of a program. The book also guides readers on how to remove unnecessary complexity from their work. Through examples and principles, it shows how good coding habits can improve software quality. Overall, Clean Code is a valuable resource for anyone w
ho wants to become a more disciplined and effective programmer.
